data.description: Priced to sell. Approx 20 mins to either Kingston and Bainbridge ferries. NEW CARPETS through out.   3 bedroom 2.5 bath home, welcoming entry from a 42 ft covered cedar front porch. Home has plenty of parking with oversized 2 car detached garage. Property has room for an RV. House sits on private 0.51 acre lot.  Enjoy entertaining on your large stone patio. Kitchen has beautiful maple cabinets, pantry and stainless appliances. Spacious formal living & dining room. Great room just off kitchen, good size laundry room with exit to oversized 2 car detached garage. Huge main suite with walk in closet. An extra bonus room upstairs would be perfect for additional walk in closet or an office.
